OL,3,C'Unrest is not welcome' says family of
OL,4,Cman stabbed in Belfast attack
OL,6,FThe family of Stephen Ogilvy, the man
OL,7,Fstabbed on Monday night in north
OL,8,FBelfast, have said they do not want
OL,9,Fthe attack to "divide people or fuel
OL,10,Fhostility" after rioters took to the
OL,11,Fstreets of Belfast on Tuesday evening.
OL,13,FThe reaction to the incident saw mobs
OL,14,Fset homes, a bus and cars on fire,
OL,15,Fwith people targeted based on their
OL,16,Frace.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
