OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781187095
OL,3,C'Unrest is not welcome' says family of
OL,4,Cman stabbed in Belfast attack
OL,6,FIn a statement, the family said: "We
OL,7,Fare completely devastated by the
OL,8,Fhorrific attack on our loved one on
OL,9,FKinnaird Avenue. This has been a
OL,10,Fmassive shock to our whole family, and
OL,11,Fright now, our only priority is being
OL,12,Fat his bedside and helping him recover.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
