PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781187095
OL,3,C'Unrest is not welcome' says family of
OL,4,Cman stabbed in Belfast attack
OL,6,F"We want to say a profound thank you
OL,7,Fto the local people who bravely
OL,8,Fstepped in during the attack. Your
OL,9,Fquick actions absolutely saved his
OL,10,Flife, and we will never forget what
OL,11,Fyou did for him in that moment. We
OL,12,Falso want to thank the emergency
OL,13,Fservices and the doctors and nurses
OL,14,Flooking after him.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781187095
OL,3,C'Unrest is not welcome' says family of
OL,4,Cman stabbed in Belfast attack
OL,6,F"We are aware of the tensions and
OL,7,Ftalk of protests following this
OL,8,Fincident. We want to make it
OL,9,Fabsolutely clear that overnight unrest
OL,10,Fis not welcome, and peaceful protest
OL,11,Fis the only way forward. We have many
OL,12,Fmigrants who make a deeply valuable
OL,13,Fcontribution to our country, including
OL,14,Fin our healthcare system and
OL,15,Fhospitality sector and we depend on
OL,16,Fthem to make our country work. We do
OL,17,Fnot want this terrible tragedy to be
OL,18,Fused to divide people or fuel
OL,19,Fhostility.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
