PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781187095
OL,3,C'Unrest is not welcome' says family of
OL,4,Cman stabbed in Belfast attack
OL,6,F"We are asking the media and the
OL,7,Fpublic to please give us some space.
OL,8,FWe need privacy to focus on our family
OL,9,Fright now, without cameras or people
OL,10,Fspeculating about what happened. If
OL,11,Fyou know anything at all about the
OL,12,Fattack, or saw anything strange near
OL,13,FKinnaird Avenue, please go to the
OL,14,Fpolice.
OL,16,F"Thank you for respecting our
OL,17,Fprivacy."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
