PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781187095
OL,3,C'Unrest is not welcome' says family of
OL,4,Cman stabbed in Belfast attack
OL,6,FHadi Alodid, 30, with an address at
OL,7,FDuncairn Avenue in Belfast, has
OL,8,Fappeared before the city's
OL,9,Fmagistrates' court on Wednesday
OL,10,Fmorning and is charged with attempted
OL,11,Fmurder, threatening to kill an NHS
OL,12,Fradiographer on the same day and with
OL,13,Fthe possession of a knife.
OL,15,FThe court heard the victim, Stephen
OL,16,FOgilvy has lost his left eye and has
OL,17,Fsevere damage to his right eye in the
OL,18,Fattack as well as deep cuts to his
OL,19,Fhead and face, and long lacerations on
OL,20,Fhis back.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
