OL,3,C'Unrest is not welcome' says family of
OL,4,Cman stabbed in Belfast attack
OL,6,FThere were a number of protests around
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland in the wake of the
OL,8,Fattack. While some passed off
OL,9,Fpeacefully, violence did flare in
OL,10,Fpockets.
OL,12,FPolice are to increase numbers on the
OL,13,Fstreets on Wednesday and political
OL,14,Fleaders to meet to discuss the matter.
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
OL,19,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,20,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/7
